      <textAnnotation id="sid-810CB3DF-1F5C-4C23-9A0E-194D563D0EB5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If the kit are on on blocked stock from previous process
Buyer will manually create sub con PR/PO
Warehouse will need to unblock the stock to deliver</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2C4245AB-E38E-487F-8348-2E1AE9414081" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>For kit build VAS orders requiring that kits are immediately sent out for cleaning before being sent to factory (aka “Pre-Cleaning Process”), Buyer will have created a Sub-Con PO for the Kit MMID for the appropriate Supplier</text>
      </textAnnotation>
